{
  "stem": "4967.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And they looked at me, and they said, right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Go-- go to the left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And in the evening, they let us go back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "These who went to the right had a terrible fate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "They were shot or burned, maybe both.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And the ghetto started to become smaller and smaller.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "People had to vacate buildings, the houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "The ghetto consisted of three blocks of flats and mostly houses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But in the houses, didn't stay one family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Maybe five families stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "Maybe people shared a room, two or three families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "Children, were not so many left already because they took away in the-- in the children's action, the women's, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And we survived this action.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "Action means they come to liquidate people, to take away people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And we came home, and we made hot water, maybe a piece of bread we still had at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And I survived this agony too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And we knew that now it was a method of liquidation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And we find out there is-- there is a ghetto in Poland, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I can't remember if we know that the Jewish people rose against the Germans in 1943.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "I can't remember the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "But we knew that it's going to be an uprising to stand against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and I find out that there is a youth organization, who they call themselves partisans, visiting the ghetto from time to time and taking away young people to be trained [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as-- as fighters against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
